reviewText: THIS WAS THE FASTEST I RECEIVED A PRODUCT FROM AMAZON!!!! MY DVD LOOKS BRAND NEW, I WILL BUY FROM YOU ALL AGAIN AND THANKS!!

HOW CAN YOU BEAT 5 MOVIES FOR THE PRICE OF 1...2 STONER MOVIES (HALF BAKED & HOW HIGH),CB4(A RAP PARODY MOVIE),TRIPPIN(MY ALL TIME FAVORITE DAYDREAMING MOVIE) & SCREWED(THE NAME SAYS IT ALL)...I LOVE THIS COLLECTION...ALL THE MOVIES ARE FAVES OF MINE...THANKS AMAZON..YOU ARE BETTER THAN EVERYBODY ELSE

I really felt I got what I paid for and more. It arrived very fast, in mint condition. Have already watched them all. Discs play great. Half Baked and How High are on same disc, you pick the movie you want from the first screen that comes up (nice). Go for it!

Is it just me or do I love the nostalgia of watching stoner movies from my high school days?  They always seem to bring me back to a time when life was simple and I did not have car payments and mortgage bills. I bought this film collection on the sole purpose it included the film CB4. Although such a cheesy movie, to this day my high school friends and I can still quote this movie line by line and rap to the songs. HALF BAKED and HOW HIGH are also a plus with this collection. Well worth the money :)
Good Movies = good times! Half Baked is where I fell I love with Dave Chappelle so get this collection if your a "smoker" or if you just love retarded movies!
